{"tid":1047872,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［NBA］如果出年交易lbj，換你愛隊最強球員，你制唔制？","createTime":"2019-03-05T09:07:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T10:00:43.000Z","uid":113326,"like":9,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"fe99c7e6f01f68bb2e8dc5fb58afaec5893798d3","tid":1047872,"uid":113326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T09:07:17.000Z","msg":"如果lbj單換你愛隊最強球員，你肯唔肯？<br />\n如果唔肯，換第二最強球員得唔得？如此類推<br />\n<br />\n以雷霆為例，如果將lbj 換Paul george （MVP shares高過Westbrook），okc一定唔肯<br />\n<br />\n其次，lbj單換westbrook，okc都唔肯<br />\n<br />\n再次，lbj換adams，okc先至肯換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n純粹傾下lbj交易價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n註一：lbj 出年仲有三年約，分別37.5m，39m，41m（player option）<br />\n<br />\n註二：今次交易唔洗再驚lbj唔續約，第四年player option，由於lbj無法再簽頂薪，大機會opt in"},{"pid":"1801a5bf016c7fbfa82fc1fb1cf5f58cd7e4a588","tid":1047872,"uid":35032,"like":8,"dislike":23,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T09:09:49.000Z","msg":"都係玩玩具姐"},{"pid":"cd2976e691e0441de0eb2f7d09ad090fe31d487b","tid":1047872,"uid":93932,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T09:13:35.000Z","msg":"冇咩人會要，真係終於都老啦，湖人都唔駛trade佢，占士入湖人都唔知幫湖人賺多幾多錢，未來又仲有咁多有潛力既人唔洗驚"},{"pid":"7d7470a751151c81343d7abaee386765af1e83ae","tid":1047872,"uid":113326,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T09:14:24.000Z","msg":"太陽為例<br />\n<br />\n因為lbj 唔係帶任何隊伍都保底決賽，舊年湖人43%勝率，今年lbj都帶唔入季後賽，包尾既太陽更加冇可能。<br />\n<br />\n所以，新人潛力更重要。<br />\n<br />\nayton booker 有潛力，單換lbj，唔值。<br />\nwarren 25 歲超值合同，唔知應唔應該破壞太陽薪金結構而換。"},{"pid":"169050e6e0176e5ff46428b8cecb4dbbaebade8c","tid":1047872,"uid":36372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T09:43:41.000Z","msg":"去勇士"},{"pid":"3f5ae154eacb80d31f4dc5be65d02a4bf714f24f","tid":1047872,"uid":45857,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T09:55:03.000Z","msg":"lbj換cp3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4a54ab1f8849ba686994e5fe2f99d4fcd28167b","tid":1047872,"uid":63952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f5ae154eacb80d31f4dc5be65d02a4bf714f24f","tid":1047872,"uid":45857,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T09:55:03.000Z","msg":"lbj換cp3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T10:07:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊撚到強"},{"pid":"99d42274ac8f02a7a90c9806e609cc82eca7dfef","tid":1047872,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T10:13:24.000Z","msg":"騎士換love"},{"pid":"3daa809fec1507817cd16c3fd5d030236faab061","tid":1047872,"uid":28809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T10:25:04.000Z","msg":"廢老換jr deal!"},{"pid":"abedd21163ee5f026ad59899f2ee69e0828c60ea","tid":1047872,"uid":61082,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T10:25:59.000Z","msg":"馬刺，前提一換一<br />\n應該都唔會搞得成，大家都一樣咁老<br />\n交易嚟又破壞默契又洗多一大舊錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nLBJ換阿德烈治不了<br />\nLBJ換迪羅沙都係麻麻，而家化學反應唔錯，信波波會教好迪羅沙好過<br />\nLBJ換基哥其實算係最合適，但係出年基哥合約到期，續唔續約馬刺都係問題，更加唔好講用嚟交易<br />\n<br />\n除非占士返老還童去返廿零歲嗰陣，否則馬刺應該都係穩中求勝，唔會搞大手筆"},{"pid":"175f9aa03ec712dc8be053d2798a6f8c3c4deffc","tid":1047872,"uid":143400,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"abedd21163ee5f026ad59899f2ee69e0828c60ea","tid":1047872,"uid":61082,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T10:25:59.000Z","msg":"馬刺，前提一換一<br />\n應該都唔會搞得成，大家都一樣咁老<br />\n交易嚟又破壞默契又洗多一大舊錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nLBJ換阿德烈治不了<br />\nLBJ換迪羅沙都係麻麻，而家化學反應唔錯，信波波會教好迪羅沙好過<br />\nLBJ換基哥其實算係最合適，但係出年基哥合約到期，續唔續約馬刺都係問題，更加唔好講用嚟交易<br />\n<br />\n除非占士返老還童去返廿零歲嗰陣，否則馬刺應該都係穩中求勝，唔會搞大手筆"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T10:31:48.000Z","msg":"lbj單換你個3件垃圾，弱智嘅都唔會deal啦，你個3件勁